<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="3Dec1904"><font color="red">3 December 1904</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> 45-7 (JJ to Stanislaus Joyce): Via Giulia 2, Pola, Austria. <br>I am half way through Chapter XIII and if you like will send you Chaps XII and XIII before Xmas for your opinion. [&hellip;]Do you ever see Dana and did they print my obscene song &lsquo;Bid Adieu&rsquo;? I read Nora Chap XI which she thought remarkable but she cares nothing for my art. Ask hairy Jaysus [Francis Sheehy-Skeffington] what am I to do? He ought to know.</div>
